The JSON Convert demo wiki ships three long-form guides:

* [[Profile Guide]] -- what a profile is, anatomy, building one by hand or with the editor.
* [[Console Guide]] -- the Console workflow end to end: loading source, picking a profile, converting, reviewing the staging area, applying.
* [[Transforms Guide]] -- how transforms reshape values, the built-ins shipped with the plugin, and writing your own (transcludes the Usage guide's transform chapters).

For additional reference -- recipes, error codes, plugin internals -- see the [[Usage guide|$:/plugins/crosseye/json-convert/usage]] in the plugin itself.

